839
00:39:29,019 --> 00:39:30,019
By the time the physician arrived,

840
00:39:30,019 --> 00:39:31,459
Mr. Wu Shan would be dead.

841
00:39:32,419 --> 00:39:33,539
You've grown up on the battlefield.

842
00:39:33,820 --> 00:39:35,619
